        <!DOCTYPE html>
        <html lang="en">

        <head>
            <meta charset="UTF-8">
            <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
            <title>Courses</title>
            <style>
                * {
                    margin: 0;
                    padding: 0;
                }

                .courses {
                    position: relative;
                    top: 30vh;
                    display: flex;
                    justify-content: space-evenly;
                    /* align-items: flex-start; */
                    height: 77vh;
                }

                .courses .card {
                    width: 25vw;
                    height: 4rem;
                    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px 1px var(--color5);
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    text-align: center;
                    background-color: var(--color4);
                    transition: height 0.8s ease-in-out;
                    overflow: hidden;
                }

                .courses .card h1 {
                    height: 4rem;
                    padding: 15px 0;
                    border-radius: 10px;
                    background-color: var(--color3);
                    color: var(--color1);
                    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px 1px var(--color1);
                }

                .courses .card p {
                    /* height: 0; */
                    padding: 20px;
                    text-align: justify;
                    color: var(--color1);
                    /* overflow: hidden; */
                }

                .courses .card .active {
                    height: fit-content;
                }
            </style>
        </head>

        <body>
            <div class="courses">
                <div class="card">
                    <h1>B.TECH</h1>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorem odio ab optio tempore quis sit
                        aliquam voluptate cum, autem dicta, officiis amet? Pariatur vel nulla, animi debitis quidem
                        exercitationem? Et quis incidunt dicta quae doloribus quasi fugiat reprehenderit exercitationem,
                        architecto pariatur quos impedit, commodi maiores animi deserunt, ullam vel quia!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h1>M.TECH</h1>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Saepe reiciendis accusamus nemo nulla
                        ducimus et voluptates ad esse adipisci libero blanditiis perferendis asperiores, consectetur
                        voluptas tempore molestiae repellat excepturi quis veniam placeat corrupti. Veniam architecto
                        ipsum, incidunt rem alias omnis beatae atque laudantium sequi tempora vitae. Illum magni beatae
                        odit.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h1>MCA</h1>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Voluptatum exercitationem consequuntur
                        architecto unde neque tempore, non dolorem eveniet perferendis sequi, illo ducimus natus
                        molestiae quaerat harum temporibus quasi a. Officiis quam delectus ratione impedit repellendus
                        inventore dolor, quaerat itaque assumenda commodi maiores repellat blanditiis, sit, facilis
                        vitae nam harum. Dignissimos.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <script>
                const cards = document.querySelectorAll(".card");

                cards.forEach(card => {
                    card.addEventListener("click", () => {
                        // card.classList.toggle("active");
                        if(card.style.height != "65vh") card.style.height = "65vh"
                        else card.style.height = "4rem";

                    });
                });
            </script>
        </body>

        </html>